metadata.name: Voxel Kittens #7620
metadata.description:
The "Voxel Kittens" art collection features pixelated cat figures in various suspicious and enigmatic eyes.
The cats have a distinct 3D 8-bit aesthetic and seem to be up to something mischievous. The collection is both playful and intriguing, leaving viewers wondering about the hidden meanings behind the cats' intentions.

10,000 Unique colorful design Kittens jpegs.

By Pumpkinz & HKDAO Collective
